==English==

===Etymology===
Coined by Gerry and Sylvia Anderson for the TV series ''[[w:Thunderbirds|Thunderbirds]]'', from {{m|en|fab}}, clipping of {{m|en|fabulous}}. Popular backronyms include "full acknowledgement of broadcast" and "fully advised and briefed".

